Skills Required:     - Bachelor degree in Computer Science, Mathematics, Bioinformatics, Health Informatics, Biotechnology, Clinical Research or a related technical field or equivalent practical experience   
  - Hands-on experience in implementing machine learning techniques using Python, R etc. Computer Vision    
  - Expertise in analytical concepts such as - Regression, Clustering,&amp;nbsp;Classification, Tree based models, and/or other machine learning techniques&amp;nbsp;   
  - An understanding of Deep Learning techniques (CNNs, RNNs, GANs, Reinforcement Learning)&amp;nbsp;   
  - A high-level understanding of automation on a cloud environment is a plus. Google Cloud and/or AWS experience preferred   
  - Working knowledge of healthcare industry and regulatory requirements (regulatory reporting and compliance, privacy and security)   
  - Great analytical and quantitative skills   
  - Ability to think creatively and work well both as an individual contributor and as part of teams across multiple locations   
  - Strong communication skills and the ability to simplify the complexity of various algorithms&amp;nbsp;   
  - Demonstrated exceptional abilities in some areas of their life and will raise the effectiveness of&amp;nbsp;your team. In short, we are looking for a “Difference Maker”   
   Roles and Responsibilities:     - Be/Become a Machine Learning and Artificial Intelligence expert and apply cutting edge research technologies to solve real world business problems   
  - Work with various client stakeholders understand and evaluate their business pain points and identify areas where data science and analytics can be the solution&amp;nbsp;   
  - Develop high-level solution architectures and design ML/AI applications&amp;nbsp;   
  - Work with data science and ML engineering teams to build, test, and assess models to predict and optimize business outcomes&amp;nbsp;   
  - Work closely with delivery manager and team members, across multiple locations, to ensure seamless delivery and communication cadences&amp;nbsp;   
  - Communicate complex concepts and insights in a clear and concise manner   
  - Maintain an entrepreneurial spirit as you learn new ways to solve problems
